 <title>Некогаш сликите зборуваат повеќе од текст</title>
 <link>http://novica.discindo.org/mk/node/874</link>
 <description>&lt;section class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-1 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/5&quot;&gt;македонија&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/210&quot;&gt;прислушување&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/209&quot;&gt;комуникации&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/74&quot;&gt;закони&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;https://www.flickr.com/photos/novica/37334012364/in/dateposted-public/&quot; title=&quot;Screenshot_20171026_195906&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4510/37334012364_a1b34e7361_z.jpg&quot; width=&quot;452&quot; height=&quot;507&quot; alt=&quot;Screenshot_20171026_195906&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
